                            <i class="fas fa-star text-warning"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star text-warning"></i>
                            <i class="fas fa-star text-warning"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="review-text">"Service tiptop! My order arrived so fast and the abang rider was super friendly. Highly recommended!"</p>
                        <div class="review-author mt-auto">
